Lopinavir 800 mg ( or 10 mg/kg ) per day and Ritonavir 200 mg ( or 2.5 mg/kg ) per day plus Oseltamivir 300 mg ( or 4-6 mg /kg ) per day In moderate to critically ill COVID19; 
